          <li><a href="http://jomrcr.svbtle.com/notes-lean-analytics" target="_blank" class="colorful">Analytics</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="date-img">
          <h2 class="date darkgrey">Summer 2014 - NYC</h2>
          <div class="underline colorful"></div>
          <img src="http://www.urbansplatter.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/nyc001.jpg" alt="NYC">
        </div>

        <p>I was interning at a tech startup in Chelsea called Noom that makes health conscious mobile apps. I was helping redesign the experience behind their core offering, a premium weight loss app for iOS and Android.</p>

        <ul>
          <li><a href="http://jomrcr.svbtle.com/product-debt" target="_blank" class="colorful">Rapid prototyping</a></li>
          <li>UX Research</li>
          <li><a href="http://jomrcr.svbtle.com/notes-the-lean-startup" target="_blank" class="colorful">Lean Startups</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="date-img">
          <h2 class="date">Fall 2013 - SF</h2>
          <div class="underline colorful"></div>
          <img src="https://a2.muscache.com/locations/uploads/city/hero/20/0_4195_350_2532_hero_USA_SF_Skylines_05_mb.jpg" alt="SF">
        </div>

        <p>I was interning downtown as a web developer at the social networking company ifwe (formerly called Tagged). I focused on the front-end, helping build new features for Chat and Activity Feed.</p>

        <ul>
          <li><a href="http://jomrcr.svbtle.com/frankenblog" target="_blank" class="colorful">Blogging</a></li>
