        </ul>

        <div class="date-img">
          <h2 class="date">Winter 2013 - Austin</h2>
          <div class="underline colorful"></div>
          <img src="http://www.tcainstitute.com/Images/iStock_000003243029LakeAustin.jpg" alt="Austin">
        </div>

        <p>My first internship was as a software engineer at Bazaarvoice, a SaaS company providing ratings and reviews for e-commerce websites. I was helping rebuild their back-end in Node.js, and ironing out accessibility requirements on the front-end.</p>

        <ul>
